org.ensembl.datamodel.Persistent

Packages that use Persistent
org.ensembl.compara.datamodel Data types that are unique to ensembl compara databases such as Homology and GenomicAlign. 
org.ensembl.datamodel Data types that appear in the core ensembl databases such as Genes, Exons and Karyotypes and various support classes such as Location. 
org.ensembl.datamodel.impl Implementation of core ensembl data types. 
org.ensembl.util Utility classes. 
org.ensembl.variation.datamodel Data types that are unique to ensembl variation databases such as Variation, Allele and Genotype.
